## 💡 Design Patterns to Consider

| Pattern | Where | Why |
|---------|-------|-----|
| **State Pattern** | Machine states | IDLE, SELECTING, AWAITING_PAYMENT, DISPENSING |
| **Strategy Pattern** | Payment handling | Coins vs Notes (if different validation) |
| **Singleton** | VendingMachine | One machine instance |
| **Factory Pattern** | Coffee creation | Different coffees from recipes |
| **Chain of Responsibility** | Change dispensing | Similar to ATM note dispenser |

