## 📦 Entities to Implement

### Enums
- `MachineState`: IDLE, AWAITING_PAYMENT, DISPENSING
- `DrinkType`: ESPRESSO, LATTE, CAPPUCCINO
- `Ingredient`: COFFEE, MILK, WATER, SUGAR
- `Coin`: ONE, TWO, FIVE, TEN
- `Note`: TEN, TWENTY

### Classes
- `Drink`: type, price, recipe
- `Inventory`: tracks ingredient levels
- `CashBox`: stores collected money
- `ChangeDispenser`: returns excess payment
- `VendingMachineState`: abstract class for State Pattern
- `VendingMachine`: Singleton, main orchestrator

